{"tid":2041710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金鐘站附近路軌有積水　海洋公園至金鐘9分鐘一班車","createTime":"2020-05-29T11:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T12:13:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c3af865163dc5970ddc8a472f4d42856faab9b","tid":2041710,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"2020-05-29 HKT 19:36<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，南港島綫金鐘站附近路軌範圍有積水，維修人員正在現場處理。<br />\n<br />\n現時南港島綫來往海怡半島站和海洋公園站維持5分鐘一班車，來往海洋公園站和金鐘站維持9分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n由於候車時間可能較長，港鐵呼籲乘客為行程預留充裕時間。"},{"pid":"eaeb07906105aaf7d60adf66afd3cf173330ec85","tid":2041710,"uid":49359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"d水邊到黎"},{"pid":"9b78a18892ed5e38c71e184f9dfd558cbdf74456","tid":2041710,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"水浸就水浸啦"},{"pid":"5e64cbf8cfa5581cdc51cfa478b2d2cb02ba806a","tid":2041710,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"黨鐵高潮"}]}